"""Kaggle kernel: Track B SAC/TD3 off-policy algorithm-scope screen.

Closes a reviewer objection flagged in the lit-review positioning doc: the
paper uses PPO exclusively (with RecurrentPPO as a comparator); off-policy
continuous-control algorithms such as SAC and TD3 are natural robustness
checks. Runs both at the exact canonical Track B protocol (control_v1 reward,
adaptive_benchmark_v2 risk, obs v7, h104, 5 seeds x 60k timesteps) so results
are directly comparable to the canonical PPO run at
outputs/experiments/track_b_gain_2026-06-30/top_tier_confirm_v3_output/
track_b_top_tier_confirm_5seed_60k_h104/ (order_ret_excel PPO win vs best
static, +8-9% relative at this scale/protocol family).
"""

